I saw  both xXx movies when first released on DVD and recently The Return of Xander Cage in Ultra HD so I might as well collect the first two films on Blu Ray for a great  price , picture & sound ,  on the first movie Cage goes under cover to infiltrate a ruthless Russian gang anarchy 99 armed with a deadly virus poisonous gas missile in a small sub that can destroy an entire city , great action stunts fighting sequences , shoot outs and special affects  .
As for the sequel Vin Diesel is replaced by Ice Cube about corruption and a coupe against the government with great action stunts , shoot outs , fighting sequences , explosions , tanks ,  awesome Mustangs and special affects  , The sequel is better than the some of the negative reviews I read  , Two Blu Ray movies for a great price , worth buying .
